title: How Pennsylvanians are feeling about the economy ahead of Trump's rally
description: Affordability was a huge theme of Trump's campaign and is top of mind for the GOP as he heads to Pennsylvania for a rally. How are Pennsylvanians feeling, and can the GOP salvage its economic message?
